.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-OPEN" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-open \- open a Lightning payment channel
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-open
.I pubkey sat
.RB [ --push-sat
.IR sat ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Opens a channel to a connected peer by calling
.BR lightning-cli (1)
.BR fundchannel .
The peer must already be connected (see
.BR lightning-peer-connect (1)).
.PP
Returns JSON
.B {"txid":"...","channel_id":"...","sat":<int>}
on success.
.TP
.B --push-sat N
Push N satoshis to the remote side at open time.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Channel open transaction broadcast.
.TP
.B 5
Open failed (peer not connected, insufficient funds, etc.).
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-channel-close (1),
.BR lightning-peer-connect (1)
